    dc:description "FIGURES 1–9. Rheocricotopus (Psilocricotopus) sirventorum Andersen & Mendes, 2012, adult female (1, 2), pupa (3–5) and larva (6–9). 1, genitalia, ventral view; 2, genitalia, dorsal view; 3, frontal apotome and prefrons; 4, thoracic horn and precorneals; 5, abdominal tergites; 6, antenna; 7, labrum and epipharyngeal area; 8, mandible; 9, mentum." ;
